# Build context is the Syntra repo root (with Lang/ now a sibling
# subdirectory inside it). target/ is the dominant offender — without
# this exclusion the Docker build context balloons to ~5GB.
**/target/
**/*.lyc
**/*.lycap
**/lycan-store/
**/.git/
**/.env
**/.DS_Store
**/node_modules/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.terraform/
docs/site/site/
